sub_title: Biochemistry| Molecular Biology | Research and Education
summary:
I am a passionate scientist with expertise in biomedical-research. Throughout my research career, I have  planned, led and completed multiple research projects successfully. 

I am experienced in working in Molecular Biology and Biochemistry research and education. Skilled in Cell culture, Organoid culture, Molecular Biology and Bioinformatics. 

I enjoy working on creative projects in the field of life sciences towards a better understanding of diseases and exploring new therapeutic applications.
